member.summary: Encapsulates request for getting the sum of the quantities for unposted transactions.

member.param: The Product Warehouse pairs to query for.

member.name: P:Microsoft.Dynamics.Commerce.Runtime.DataServices.Messages.GetProductWarehouseInventoryUnpostedQuantityDataRequest.UnpostedQuantities

member.name: P:Microsoft.Dynamics.Commerce.Runtime.DataServices.Messages.GetProductWarehouseInventoryUnpostedQuantityDataRequest.SearchCriteria
member.summary: Gets the Last Inventory Transaction (recId) that was created before the the last Product Availability job.
member.remarks: This tells the Sum calculation which transactions to include and exclude (which are already included in the Inventory values). We set this value in the request, because it's possible that the 1130 CDX job could retrieve more data between when we fetched the inventory values and when we request the sum.
